"{\"uid\": \"scvnews.com-scv-water-polo-players-compete-in-usa-water-polo-junior-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"[Sign Up Now] to Receive Our FREE Daily SCVTV-SCVNews Digest by E-Mail  Five athletes from the Santa Clarita Valley have participated in their first USA Water Polo Junior Olympics Water Polo Tournament.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 202, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 95, \"end\": 115, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santa_Clarita_Valley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Santa Clarita Valley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santa_Clarita_Valley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santa_Clarita_Valley\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The athletes participated at the event held at the end of July in the San Francisco Bay area.\", \"from\": 203, \"to\": 296, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Caleb Kornbluth, Ellis Sacchetto, Paul Gommel, Jackson Brosche and Emory Brown, representing the SCV Waves, triumphed in four games against competitors from all across the United States, according to a news release from the Santa Clarita Waves water polo organization.\", \"from\": 298, \"to\": 566, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 298, \"end\": 303, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kings_of_Leon\", \"score\": 0.9999530886740289, \"rank\": 4.596622509758194e-05, \"text\": \"Caleb\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kings_of_Leon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kings_of_Leon\"}, {\"begin\": 315, \"end\": 320, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Albert_Ellis\", \"score\": 0.9538987966660138, \"rank\": 0.04820530566068655, \"text\": \"Ellis\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Albert_Ellis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Albert_Ellis\"}, {\"begin\": 345, \"end\": 352, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Jackson\", \"score\": 0.9164241302724757, \"rank\": 0.08014501548412618, \"text\": \"Jackson\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Jackson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Jackson\"}, {\"begin\": 470, \"end\": 483, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9909499663780308, \"rank\": 0.007208580427344429, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 522, \"end\": 535, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santa_Clarita_Valley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.810332444762712e-37, \"text\": \"Santa Clarita\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santa_Clarita_Valley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santa_Clarita_Valley\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Before making their way to Northern California for the main events, the players first competed throughout Los Angeles and Ventura County to qualify for the tournament.\", \"from\": 568, \"to\": 735, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 674, \"end\": 685, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greater_Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9662993855043531, \"rank\": 0.034875142814572706, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greater_Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greater_Los_Angeles\"}, {\"begin\": 690, \"end\": 704, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ventura_County_Fire_Department\", \"score\": 0.9999999999015472, \"rank\": 9.845858075227876e-11, \"text\": \"Ventura County\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ventura_County_Fire_Department\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ventura_County_Fire_Department\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Throughout the four-day tournament, the team displayed unwavering determination and perseverance,\\\" said officials from the Santa Clarita Valley Water Polo Club.\", \"from\": 737, \"to\": 898, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 861, \"end\": 881, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santa_Clarita_Valley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Santa Clarita Valley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santa_Clarita_Valley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santa_Clarita_Valley\"}, {\"begin\": 882, \"end\": 892, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Water_polo\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 1.1059456210913696e-13, \"text\": \"Water Polo\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Water_polo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Water_polo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They stayed together as a close-knit unit, supporting and encouraging one another both in and out of the pool.\\\"\", \"from\": 899, \"to\": 1011, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One of the highlights was when the team played two games at Stanford University.\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1093, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1073, \"end\": 1092, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stanford_University\", \"score\": 0.9965390486035249, \"rank\": 0.00347293833682419, \"text\": \"Stanford University\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stanford_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stanford_University\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The team won the final match of the Junior Olympics and finished fifth overall in the Gold Division.\", \"from\": 1095, \"to\": 1195, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1131, \"end\": 1146, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AAU_Junior_Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Junior Olympics\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AAU_Junior_Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AAU_Junior_Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are incredibly proud of our young athletes from Santa Clarita Valley who represented the SCV Waves with such skill and sportsmanship at the U.S. Water Polo Junior Olympics,\\\" said SCV Waves officals.\", \"from\": 1197, \"to\": 1399, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1249, \"end\": 1269, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santa_Clarita_Valley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Santa Clarita Valley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santa_Clarita_Valley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santa_Clarita_Valley\"}, {\"begin\": 1290, \"end\": 1293, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sons_of_Confederate_Veterans\", \"score\": 0.999999496225782, \"rank\": 5.0377448480477e-07, \"text\": \"SCV\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sons_of_Confederate_Veterans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sons_of_Confederate_Veterans\"}, {\"begin\": 1346, \"end\": 1356, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Water_polo\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 1.1059456210913696e-13, \"text\": \"Water Polo\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Water_polo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Water_polo\"}, {\"begin\": 1357, \"end\": 1372, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AAU_Junior_Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Junior Olympics\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AAU_Junior_Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AAU_Junior_Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 1380, \"end\": 1383, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sons_of_Confederate_Veterans\", \"score\": 0.999999496225782, \"rank\": 5.0377448480477e-07, \"text\": \"SCV\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sons_of_Confederate_Veterans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sons_of_Confederate_Veterans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The SCV Waves, which includes girls and boys aged 8 to 17 years old, invite others who share a passion for swimming and